for the use case that you want a constraint on the telephone field of the number of digits that can be entered and specific display formats should be available, this can be achieved by using custom clientlibs and you can apply rules.

A sample of one such script for reference is below which can be modified and tweaked according to your use case as this is just a sample.

The script below is attached to the exit event of a Text Field with a maximum length of 14. The script also enables the entry of <tel:1234567890|123 456 7890>, also.
```if (!(this.isNull)) {

  var str = this.rawValue;

  var regExp = /^\d{10}$/;

  if (regExp.test(str)) {

